
TO COMPILE
       1  source ./setup.sh LPP (compile with PGI)
       2 ./configure  --- to get a list of compile options for your computer
		         If your computer is not listed, you will need to add it under
			 arch/configure.defaults
       3 ./compile    --- compile the code

       4 ./clean -a   --- clean 


TO RUN:
       1  source ./setup_pgi.sh
       2  ./ARWpost.exe > wr_29112022.txt 2>&1 &
